description: This package contains the FabricObserver Application (built for .NET 6.0, SF Runtime 9.0 and above), a highly configurable and extensible resource usage watchdog service that is designed to be run in Azure Service Fabric Windows and Linux clusters. This package contains the entire application and can be used to build .NET Standard 2.0 observer plugins.
releaseNotes:
- Updated NodeObserver's Dynamic Port Range ETW impl.
- Bug fix in OSInfoLogger and new Windows port detection impl. See release notes for Microsoft.ServiceFabricApps.FabricObserver.Extensibility v3.2.3 nupkg for details.
title: Service Fabric FabricObserver Application
